<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About - CryptoInfoHub</title>
    <style>
        /* Reset default margins and paddings */
        
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        /* Body styles */
        
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            /* Light grey background */
            color: #333;
            /* Dark grey text color */
            line-height: 1.6;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        /* Header styles */
        
        header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        header h1 {
            color: #007bff;
            /* Blue heading color */
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        /* Main section styles */
        
        main {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        /* Overview section styles */
        
        #overview {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            /* White background for overview section */
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            /* Soft shadow effect */
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        #overview h2 {
            color: #007bff;
            /* Blue heading color */
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        #overview p {
            color: #666;
            /* Medium grey text color */
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        /* Features section styles */
        
        #features {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            /* White background for features section */
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            /* Soft shadow effect */
        }
        
        #features h2 {
            color: #007bff;
            /* Blue heading color */
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        /* Article styles */
        
        article {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        article h3 {
            color: #0056b3;
            /* Dark blue heading color */
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        article p {
            color: #666;
            /* Medium grey text color */
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        
        article strong {
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <header>
        <h1>About This Project</h1>
    </header>
    <main>
        <section id="overview">
            <h2>Overview</h2>
            <p>Welcome to the <strong>CryptoInfoHub</strong>! This platform is designed to provide comprehensive and real-time information about various cryptocurrencies. Whether you're a seasoned trader or a crypto enthusiast, our website offers valuable
                insights into the world of digital currencies.</p>
        </section>
        <section id="features">
            <h2>Key Features</h2>
            <article>
                <h3>Live Ticker Data</h3>
                <p><strong>Description:</strong> Enter a cryptocurrency ticker symbol to retrieve live data such as symbol, price (24h), volume (24h), and last trade price.</p>
                <p><strong>Benefit:</strong> Track specific cryptocurrencies and monitor their performance over time, helping you stay updated with the latest market trends.</p>
            </article>
            <article>
                <h3>Order Book Visualization</h3>
                <p><strong>Description:</strong> Fetch the order book data for a specific cryptocurrency ticker symbol. The platform displays bids and asks data, including prices, quantities, and numbers, in a structured format.</p>
                <p><strong>Benefit:</strong> Understand current market depth and trading sentiment, providing insights into buy and sell orders for informed decision-making.</p>
            </article>
            <article>
                <h3>Ticker Information Display</h3>
                <p><strong>Description:</strong> Fetch detailed information about a cryptocurrency symbol by entering its ticker. The website displays information such as base currency, counter currency, minimum price increment, minimum order size, maximum
                    order size, lot size, status, auction details, and imbalance.</p>
                <p><strong>Benefit:</strong> Access comprehensive details about specific cryptocurrencies, aiding users in making informed trading decisions.</p>
            </article>
        </section>
    </main>
    <%- include('footer.ejs') %>

</body>

</html>